      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything i spent the last decade working on... it was all for nothing. the data was flawed from the start. i've spent my entire adult life building a legacy on a foundation of nothing. i feel like a ghost just walking around pretending to be a person. there's nothing left of me to actually exist for.",
